{"tid":918791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"GFRIEND YUJU 透過VLIVE公開近況\"想你了\"","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T15:17:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0be0ffddf870274ab7831408265d7bf24b0f53e9","tid":918791,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photo.jtbc.joins.com/news/2018/11/27/20181127192012356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.jtbc.joins.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F27%2F20181127192012356.jpg&h=5a450ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n組合GFRIEND的YUJU透過VLIVE公開了自己的近況.<br />\n<br />\nYUJU 27日突然出現在所願和信飛的NAVER V現場並露出臉龐說:&quot;我想看到Buddy(粉絲名).&quot;<br />\n<br />\n距離上個月27日最後一次參加正式活動僅過了一個月YUJU以健康開朗的樣子消除了粉絲們的憂慮.<br />\n<br />\nYUJU沒有參加行程，而是通過其他成員重新錄下有主部分的音源登上舞臺很多人對YUJU的近況感到好奇<br />\n<br />\n對此,經紀公司表示:&quot;計劃從12月開始正常參與活動.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n你班ONCE咁高興人地失蹤阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b441d12e9fd68e8c2f4e92e9baec24e0f8d64a1d","tid":918791,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"導ching覺得佢有冇整過<br />\n我淨係睇到塊面瘦咗"},{"pid":"7edab183e8573765df775ec5654da57f07e72062","tid":918791,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b441d12e9fd68e8c2f4e92e9baec24e0f8d64a1d","tid":918791,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"導ching覺得佢有冇整過<br />\n我淨係睇到塊面瘦咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"素顏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8acd8953666530b38a9dcbf7634e8c122b57de","tid":918791,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"